Installation instructions
==========================

1. Required software:

JOSM revision 6950 (http://josm.openstreetmap.de)
RoboCup Rescue Simulation Software (http://sourceforge.net/projects/roborescue)
Java1.7 JDK 
Ant

2. Building

Edit the build.properties file as follows:
  josm=<Path to JOSM-Jarfile>
  roborescue.dir=<Path to the roborescue root directory>

Run ant.

This will compile the plug-in and create the file dist/rcr-converter.jar

3. Installation

Copy jscience.jar and rcr-converter.jar into the JOSM-plug-in directory
(~/.josm/plugins/ on linux).

Start JOSM, go to settings -> plugins and enable the RCR-converter plugin.
After a restart of JOSM, everything should work.

